  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Investigate a computer [/]<br>You were just the owner of an office, but something piqued your curiosity. Understand what happened to Andy by browsing through his most personal archives and memories. OS: Memories is a short and engaging storyline about the everyday life of a game developer.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871350/extras/1f4eed2582a7d797827ffbe2f957559a.poster.avif?t=1644437929\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871350/extras/1f4eed2582a7d797827ffbe2f957559a.webm?t=1644437929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871350/extras/1f4eed2582a7d797827ffbe2f957559a.mp4?t=1644437929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Highlights: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Immerse yourself in a pleasant and intimate environment through an old computer interface.<br></li><li> Immerse yourself in Andy's life story and relive, through messages, memories and notes, the best and worst moments of his life.<br></li><li> Figure out Andy's passwords and insight into his deepest deadlocks.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871350/extras/19ae1e5901b137fbadcccbe197901901.poster.avif?t=1644437929\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871350/extras/19ae1e5901b137fbadcccbe197901901.webm?t=1644437929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871350/extras/19ae1e5901b137fbadcccbe197901901.mp4?t=1644437929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
